WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.000
You are listening to the narration for the Taj Mahal, Agra.

00:00:04.500 --> 00:00:10.000
The mausoleum was commissioned by Emperor Shah Jahan in memory of his wife Mumtaz Mahal.

00:00:10.500 --> 00:00:18.000
Observe the symmetry, calligraphy inlaid in black marble and the reflecting pools that mirror the building.
